txt.en: You have been recognized as a servant to the captains of the Palace of Eldacar!
Quest of the Palace of Eldacar -- Tier 1
Service to the captains of the Palace of Eldacar will result in the ability to find your way through the city with less effort.
Complete quests for the benefit of the Palace of Eldacar!
Edenos awaits your return to the Palace of Eldacar where he will see you rewarded for your service!
You have performed many services for the captains of the Palace of Eldacar.
